# RSA Key for TFS Login Server
#
# Generate a new key with:
#   openssl genrsa -out key.pem 1024
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit your actual key.pem to version control.
# The key.pem file is listed in .gitignore for this reason.
#
# For production deployments, use at least a 2048-bit key:
#   openssl genrsa -out key.pem 2048
